commitResults.messageBody:
Users can edit employee id via the CLI.

Employee id is used to uniquely identify each
employee in project assignments.

Allowing editing of employee id may require each project
assignment to update its value of employee id. This may
degrade performance if there are many assignments.

Let's prevent editing of employee id via the CLI.
